---
name: draft-post
description: Draft short-form posts for X, Bluesky, and Mastodon from a git trigger or description
triggers:
  - draft a post
  - write a social post
  - draft a short post
  - write a social post for all my channels
  - post about this
---

Read the skill file at `.postlane/commands/draft-post.md`, then draft posts for X, Bluesky, and Mastodon. Output sets `platforms: ["x", "bluesky", "mastodon"]` in `meta.json`.
